<p class="courseblockdesc">
Advanced topics course on specific periods or movements in Italian film and other visual media. Topics will vary.Course Information: May be repeated for a maximum of 6 hours if topic is different for each registration and with consent of the instructor. Taught in Italian. Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=ITAL%20200" title="ITAL 200" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ITAL 200');">ITAL 200</a> or <a href="/search/?P=ITAL%20201" title="ITAL 201" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ITAL 201');">ITAL 201</a> or <a href="/search/?P=ITAL%20210" title="ITAL 210" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ITAL 210');">ITAL 210</a> or the equivalent or consent of the instructor. Recommended background: <a href="/search/?P=ITAL%20280" title="ITAL 280" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ITAL 280');">ITAL 280</a>.<br/>
